# The `AppleAcceleratorTable` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This implements the Apple accelerator table format, a precursor of the DWARF 5 accelerator table format. <a href="#details">More...</a>

<CodeBlock>class llvm::AppleAcceleratorTable</CodeBlock>

## Description {#details}
